            // | CTRL |  A  |  S  |  D  |  F  |  G  |   |  H  |  J   |  K  |  L  |  ;  |  '   |
            // | SHFT |  Z  |  X  |  C  |  V  |  B  |   |  N  |  M   |  ,  |  .  |  /  | ESC  |
            //                    | GUI | LWR | SPC |   | ENT | RSE  | ALT |
            display-name = "mBAS";
            bindings = <
&kp TAB       &kp Q  &kp W  &kp E      &kp R  &kp T          &kp Y        &kp U            &kp I      &kp O    &kp P     &switch_layuot
&kp LSHFT     &kp A  &kp S  &kp D      &kp F  &kp G          &kp H        &kp J            &kp K      &kp L    &kp SEMI  &kp SQT
&mt LGUI ESC  &kp Z  &kp X  &kp C      &kp V  &kp B          &kp N        &kp M            &kp COMMA  &kp DOT  &kp FSLH  mSTG
                            &kp LCTRL  &mo 1  &lt 2 SPACE    &lt 3 ENTER  &lt 5 BACKSPACE  &kp RALT
